events.name: Texas A&M Aggies at North Carolina Tar Heels

headlines.description: — Devon Achane had two late touchdown runs, including a 76-yarder with 3:44 left that put Texas A&M ahead to stay, and the fifth-ranked Aggies beat No. 14 North Carolina 41-27 in the Orange Bowl on Saturday night to cap a winless bowl season for...
headlines.shortLinkText: Texas A&M runs past North Carolina in Orange Bowl, 41-27

events.name: Oregon Ducks at Iowa State Cyclones
Ole Miss Rebels at Indiana Hoosiers

headlines.description: — Matt Corral threw for 342 yards and two touchdowns, leading Mississippi to a 26-20 upset of seventh-ranked Indiana in the Outback Bowl on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Corral, Ole Miss take down No. 7 Indiana in Outback Bowl

events.name: NC State Wolfpack at Kentucky Wildcats

headlines.description: — A.J. Rose ran for a career-high 148 yards, Chris Rodriguez added 84 yards and two scores and Kentucky held off No. 24 North Carolina State 23-21 in a chippy TaxSlayer Gator Bowl on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Kentucky runs for 281, beats NC State 23-21 in chippy Gator
